%N A134110 Powers of 4 written backwards and sorted.
%C A134110 Could be seen as irregular table where row n lists the n-digit terms { 4^k : (n-1) log 10 < k log 4 < n log 10 }. - _M. F. Hasler_, Mar 27 2026
%t A134110 Sort[FromDigits[Reverse[IntegerDigits[#]]]&/@(4^Range[0,25])]  (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Feb 22 2011 *)
%o A134110 (PARI) A134110_first(n)=my(L=log(10)/log(4)); vecsort([A004086(4^k) | k<-[0..n\/L*L\1]])[1..n] \\ _M. F. Hasler_, Mar 27 2026
